name: PlayStation 5 Console (Slim)
reviewer: The PS5 power cable is missing from the box. The PS5 is therefore completely useless. I am very dissatisfied with Amazon.
reviews: I had to purchase another cable as the hassle of sending the whole thing back was too much of a pain.

name: PlayStation 5 Console (Slim)

name: PlayStation 5 Console (Slim)
reviewer: The PS5 power cable is missing from the box. The PS5 is therefore completely useless. I am very dissatisfied with Amazon.
reviews: This console is just amazing. You get everything from the origional ps5, except 30% smaller! You even get 200GB more than the previous Ps5. You get 1 Terabyte which is awesome! Other reviews say it's loud but i will tell you i've played many games pushing the ps5 to it's limit and i haven't heard the fan ONCE! This console is amazing and i reccomend it to all looking for a great start or addition to their gaming journey! Thanks!

name: PlayStation 5 Console (Slim)
reviews: If you enjoy the jet engine sounds of a PS4 then you are right at home with the ps5 slim.Console runs hot. Really hot and the fans are insanely loud when playing games.Genuinely disappointed with this console.

name: PlayStation 5 Console (Slim)
reviews: Maybe I just got a lemon/was unlucky but it does feel cheaply made. Will stick with my Xbox.

name: PlayStation 5 Console (Slim)
reviews: The console doesn't come with a stand, they charge you $50 for a bit of crappy plastic and the console some how runs hotter, lags more and looks worse some how.AVOID
